It contains from left to right, Megara in a pink dress and her hair in a pony tail looking at Hercules. Hercules stands in the center with his arms crossed wearing his brown outfit complete with his blue cape. To his right is Philoctetes (Phil), half man, half goat Satyr with horns. Behind all of them is Pegasus, a white winged horse with a blue mane and tail. The pin on pin element is Hades with his infamous blue "hair" cutting his eyes over at Megara, Hercules, Phil and Pegasus. Also on the pin on pin element is a blue block with gold trim and it says in yellow lettering, HERCULES 20th ANNIVERSARY, flanked by a lightening bolt on each side.
